import { createRouter, createWebHistory } from 'vue-router'
import CourseRecommendation from './components/CourseRecommendation.vue'
import LearningProgress from './components/LearningProgress.vue'
import VirtualLab from './components/VirtualLab.vue'
import CommunityDiscussion from './components/CommunityDiscussion.vue'
import UserDashboard from './components/UserDashboard.vue'
import AIRecommendation from './components/AIRecommendation.vue'
import WebRTCChat from './components/WebRTCChat.vue'
import HardwareSensor from './components/HardwareSensor.vue'

const routes = [
    { path: '/', name: 'CourseRecommendation', component: CourseRecommendation },
    { path: '/learning-progress', name: 'LearningProgress', component: LearningProgress },
    { path: '/virtual-lab', name: 'VirtualLab', component: VirtualLab },
    { path: '/community-discussion', name: 'CommunityDiscussion', component: CommunityDiscussion },
    { path: '/dashboard', name: 'UserDashboard', component: UserDashboard },
    { path: '/ai-recommendation', name: 'AIRecommendation', component: AIRecommendation },
    { path: '/webrtc-chat', name: 'WebRTCChat', component: WebRTCChat },
    { path: '/hardware-sensor', name: 'HardwareSensor', component: HardwareSensor }
]

const router = createRouter({
    history: createWebHistory(),
    routes
})

export default router
